%% Use case diagram: Monitor Health
flowchart LR
  operator((Operator))
  health[GET /health]
  db[(SQLite DB)]

  operator -->|polls endpoint| health
  health -->|SELECT 1| db
  db -->|reachable| health
  health -->|200 status: ok| operator
  db -->|unreachable| health
  health -->|503 status: error| operator
